{
  "stem": "15393.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, here I am with her and I have nothing else to wear but what I had on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was sitting there in the corner quietly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Everybody said, oh, where is she from, why-- all these questions my mother had to answer.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then walks in this tall German lady for whom my mother is sewing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she looks at me, who is this?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My mother said, this is my daughter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I told you I have a daughter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Why-- why isn't she dressed?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "What's she doing like this here?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So my mother told her, well, she came with me from the ghetto today-- she couldn't say that she'd stayed behind or anything-- she came with me from the ghetto [INAUDIBLE] and the situation is very difficult now and I don't know how we should get back and so forth.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So what do you mean she came like this, not dressed?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "How can she walk like this?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You have to put something on this child and so on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And so she was expressing some kind of sympathy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And every now and again she would come in and look at me with the most pitiable expression, you now sort of-- and I was embarrassed to look at her.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "At one point, my mother decided out of the blue she's going to ask her to take us in.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And she decided that when she has a fitting with her, she would do a fitting in a separate room so that nobody can hear and she would chance a question.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "This was very difficult because she was German.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "She did that and she asked this question.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And she, said could you possibly take us for just until this selection is over, until this quietens down a little bit?",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
